# Rocrail workspace .gitignore
#
# A Rocrail workspace holds one layout's data (plan.xml, rocrail.ini, images, ...).
# We version-control the layout itself, but ignore files Rocrail regenerates at
# runtime and resources that belong to the installed Rocrail.app instead.

# Auto-saved plan snapshots (Rocrail keeps up to maxbackup of these)
**/backup/

# Trace / log output
**/trace/
**/*.trc

# Rocrail's own .bak copies of plan.xml / rocrail.ini / etc.
**/*.bak

# Resource dirs that live inside Rocrail.app; Rocrail symlinks these into the
# workspace at runtime (they were broken translocation links on import).
**/svg
**/web

# Machine-specific / local-only
**/installpath.txt
**/lic.dat
.DS_Store
